{
  "stem": "1828.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 142.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Well, they had run out of the soup, and all we got was a boiled potato in the skin.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And people wolfed it down and ate it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And she said, children, let's sit down and eat it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Takes the same time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were some benches there on the side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we sat down, and she said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're not going to let the Germans win.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're going to peel the potato.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're not going to be less hungry if you eat the peel, and you see how thin that peel is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They sometimes get at the difference between human and animal, is-- is that thickness.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And let's show them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'll peel the potato.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It lasts us longer that way too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we thought, oh, it was all in good fun and looked at her and felt we have to go along with this.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we peeled our potato.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Somebody ate the peel immediately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It didn't really make a difference, but it is-- it is-- it's a tremendous thing to remember.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is the kind of strings that-- and-- and-- and standards that she kept on reminding us of.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't eat the peels that day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were changed to various places, and as time went on and things got worse, the reports came through occasionally.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In one of the camps that we went to, my sister was tall for her age.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they picked two or three tall girls to go to the next camp, which was-- there were some prisoners of war there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were supposed to bring some stones on a wheelbarrow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so, that's why there had to be three of them to help to-- to make a sidewalk where we were working, where we were staying.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
